{"id": 736, "genre": 1001, "title": "你的生活如何被雾霾改变了？", "description": "“现在北京的朋友约饭局都是，哎，周末来我家吃饭吧，我家净化器是blue air，另一个朋友说：我家IQ air啊，大家说：那还是去你家吃吧！”——苏更生", "record_count": 3527, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194339zEKyFQISwg9d7hUf.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-01-04T11:04:39Z", "options": [{"id": 39426, "content": "Ky", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 407825}, {"id": 39427, "content": "这个是什么软件啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 407825}, {"id": 39432, "content": "天天都有腾云驾雾的感觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 338971}, {"id": 39689, "content": "我在南方的艳阳里笑！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 345679}, {"id": 40201, "content": "雾霾吞噬了1/2的图书馆╮(╯_╰)╭", "image": "img/option/option/20160702200825jWEVJPUBno4pbyR6.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 415308}, {"id": 39435, "content": "在操场玩躲迷藏。", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 388364}, {"id": 40203, "content": "身在郑州的我默默笑笑不说话~", "image": "img/option/option/20160702200826IHPuxf5XayOmW0SN.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 415308}, {"id": 39436, "content": "一睁眼天还没亮，结果已经是大中午了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 407905}, {"id": 39437, "content": "没风被毒死，有风被吹死", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 243086}, {"id": 39440, "content": "明白了为什么要自强不“吸”。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 265401}, {"id": 39952, "content": "注意环保，保卫家园", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 413104}, {"id": 39442, "content": "石家庄人 过节不想出门所以被甩", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 246331}, {"id": 39449, "content": "避孕套销量直线上升", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 371116}, {"id": 39451, "content": "魔都的霾", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 380217}, {"id": 39452, "content": "鼻炎一个月一点不见好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 246031}, {"id": 40732, "content": "雾霾，我只吸北京的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 383972}, {"id": 39453, "content": "对这个国度已死心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 281402}, {"id": 39454, "content": "天气预报要看看污染指数，出门除了“身手钥钱”还得记得口罩", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 105318}, {"id": 39457, "content": "从未如此强烈想念过能看得见灰机和远山的艳阳天。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 102096}, {"id": 39713, "content": "今天你开空气净化器了吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 393991}, {"id": 39458, "content": "以后是不是出门都要带手电筒？赶紧备货，去发财了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 305095}, {"id": 39459, "content": "口罩随身带！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 270907}, {"id": 39464, "content": "祝你", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 408088}, {"id": 39467, "content": "并没有，挡不住我?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 347143}, {"id": 39468, "content": "你们怎么受得了！你们怎么受得了！你们怎么受得了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 360309}, {"id": 39469, "content": "想要回南方的家", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 408126}, {"id": 39726, "content": "空气新鲜也是一件妙事！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 410826}, {"id": 39472, "content": "停了近一个月的体育课?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 157246}, {"id": 40497, "content": "空气憋闷，影响心情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 405477}, {"id": 39474, "content": "冬天要么被风吹傻，要么被雾霾毒晕", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145120}, {"id": 39475, "content": "口罩成了出门标配", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 215356}, {"id": 39476, "content": "乍一看似云似雾，仔细一看有尘有烟，当雾霾轻轻袭来，昔日明媚已成过眼云烟?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 401719}, {"id": 39480, "content": "北京有雾霾吗？比河北空气好多了呢！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 401695}, {"id": 39481, "content": "以前玩儿一天回家基本不用挖鼻屎 即便挖了 也是黄黄绿绿的，现在不行哦，回家第一件事儿挖鼻屎 都是黑色", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 401813}, {"id": 39484, "content": "没人来我家吃… 小米净化器", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 401465}, {"id": 40257, "content": "Good morning（良辰） 早晨太“美好”", "image": "img/option/option/20160702200826pDsmxnf2T4LNcyFb.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 405037}, {"id": 39490, "content": "雾霾严重时感觉天地混沌，很难看出早上下午，宝宝三个多月，黑白彻底颠倒，根本出不了门", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 333314}, {"id": 39491, "content": "我在南方没有雾霾", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 323418}, {"id": 39748, "content": "得给我的各种款式的口罩们准备一个“衣柜”了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 380516}, {"id": 100421, "content": "心情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 687277}, {"id": 39494, "content": "多了一项消费—口罩", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 167381}, {"id": 39497, "content": "对人类世界兴趣减少了，更加会欣赏天空的美", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 270840}, {"id": 40525, "content": "西双版纳人想知道雾霾是什么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 417937}, {"id": 39503, "content": "眼睛疼", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 408417}, {"id": 39759, "content": "出去旅游没有想象力 还想出去？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 411490}, {"id": 39504, "content": "总得带隐形，口罩会把眼镜弄得雾蒙蒙", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 138770}, {"id": 42576, "content": "天天回家", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 431452}, {"id": 39505, "content": "体育课经常停课，好开心~~~", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 374972}, {"id": 39506, "content": "天天外卖！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 365949}, {"id": 39509, "content": "?口红可以不用了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 290593}]}